           <span class="uitext reviewText">Anyone of any age or religion.</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42777679-laura-lee-rahn?shelf=christian">christian</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42777679-laura-lee-rahn?shelf=biography">biography</a>, 
