        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3879485030" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9036918461122063866">If you yearn for a time before globalization, and some true adventure, read this. It&apos;s a true story which reads as fiction. Also a great book for women of no special talents or status or means - women who are overlooked and not valued by society. Gladys was. Did she let that stop her?! NO. (I totally would have given up in her shoes). Here is &quot;no one of importance&quot; doing amazing, grace-filled, life-saving humanitarian work in impossible conditions in a place she doesn&apos;t understand (at first), in</span>
  <span id="freeText9036918461122063866" style="display:none">If you yearn for a time before globalization, and some true adventure, read this. It's a true story which reads as fiction. Also a great book for women of no special talents or status or means - women who are overlooked and not valued by society. Gladys was. Did she let that stop her?! NO. (I totally would have given up in her shoes). Here is "no one of importance" doing amazing, grace-filled, life-saving humanitarian work in impossible conditions in a place she doesn't understand (at first), in intelligible dialects. She never seems to even consider quitting. An amazing woman. A great Int'l Women's Day recommendation. </span>
  <a data-text-id="9036918461122063866" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

